      "url": "https://github.com/pinkycollie/Nextjs-DeafAUTH",
      "description": "DeafAUTH is a focused identity and accessibility orchestration layer for Next.js apps, built to help teams reliably discover, prompt for, persist, and track accessibility needs for Deaf and hard-of-hearing learners.",
      "updated_at": "2026-07-09T16:14:51Z",
